<I c="Tutorial" i="tutorial" m="tutorials.tutorial" n="tutorial_LiveMode_TravelMoving_Moving" s="315832">
  <T n="name">0xC2617118<!--String: "Moving"--></T>
  <L n="slides">
    <U>
      <T n="image" p="InGame\UI\tutorial\Client\LiveMode\LiveMode_Moving_1.png">2f7d0004:00000000:5c19c17973d45163</T>
      <T n="text">0x5083A3A2<!--String: "So it’s time for your Sims to <b><font color='#199C2C'>move someplace new</font></b>! Perhaps they have outgrown their current home, want independence from their parents, or they’ve earned enough Simoleons to buy a fancier house. Or maybe you just want a change of scenery!"--></T>
    </U>
    <U>
      <T n="image" p="InGame\UI\tutorial\Client\LiveMode\LiveMode_Moving_2.png">2f7d0004:00000000:5c19c17973d45160</T>
      <T n="text">0xBB99D205<!--String: "You’ll find the options for moving in the Cell Phone’s <b><font color='#199C2C'>Travel app</font></b>.\n\nUse the Move Household option to move the <b><font color='#199C2C'>entire Household</font></b> to a new Lot, or Split from Household and Move option to move <b><font color='#199C2C'>parts of the Household</font></b> to a new Lot.\n\nThe Split option opens a new menu. Here you can decide <b><font color='#199C2C'>which Sims</font></b> will move out and how much <b><font color='#199C2C'>money</font></b> they will bring with them. You can press the Select another Household button to move them into another Household."--></T>
    </U>
    <U>
      <T n="image" p="InGame\UI\tutorial\Client\LiveMode\LiveMode_Moving_3.png">2f7d0004:00000000:5c19c17973d45161</T>
      <T n="text">0x5AD1BF5<!--String: "Moving will open the World Map. Lots that you can move to without any modifications are <b><font color='#199C2C'>outlined in green</font></b>. Lots <b><font color='#199C2C'>outlined in yellow</font></b> are either too expensive to buy fully furnished, or another Household already lives there.\n\nPick a Lot and press the <b><font color='#199C2C'>Confirm</font></b> button in the lower right corner to start moving!\n\nRemember that you can use the World Select button to move to another World."--></T>
    </U>
    <U>
      <T n="image" p="InGame\UI\tutorial\Client\LiveMode\LiveMode_Moving_4.png">2f7d0004:00000000:5c19c17973d45166</T>
      <T n="text">0xE37D4A6A<!--String: "Once you’ve picked a Lot, you will get options to <b><font color='#199C2C'>keep</font></b> or <b><font color='#199C2C'>sell</font></b> your current furniture (keeping the furniture puts them in the Household Inventory) and whether to buy the new Lot <b><font color='#199C2C'>furnished</font></b>, <b><font color='#199C2C'>unfurnished</font></b>, or <b><font color='#199C2C'>bulldozed</font></b>. You can see your remaining funds under the Household portrait.\n\nIf you’re moving to a Lot where someone already lives, you will get a choice whether to <b><font color='#199C2C'>move in</font></b> with them or <b><font color='#199C2C'>evict</font></b> them first.\n\n<b><font color='#199C2C'>Finalize</font></b> the move with the Purchase Home or Move In button!"--></T>
    </U>
  </L>
